headline: Imperial Oil's Q1 Earnings Beat, Revenues Miss Estimates
summary: IMO's full-year 2025 production guidance includes 280,000-290,000 bbl/d at Kearl, 150,000-160,000 bbl/d at Cold Lake and 75,000-80,000 bbl/d at Syncrude.
